The Magaluf Weekender

Season 3, Episode 1 of 6

New series. 

The show following the antics of six young people and their reps at the Spanish resort returns, with three lads from Weston-super-Mare and three girls from Liverpool staying at the Lively Hotel. New girl Ali is worried she might not have what it takes to be a rep, and there may be romance in the air for the holiday-makers
